						"Indicates action is happening right now: 'Tôi đang ăn' (I am eating)",
						"Can combine with past/future markers for past/future continuous (uncommon but valid)",
						"Often used to explain why you can't do something: 'Tôi đang bận' (I'm busy right now)"
